            <span style="color: #9b8c7a; font-size: 0.7rem;">入仓 05-26</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; font-size: 0.78rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">
            <div><span style="color: #9b8c7a;">来源</span><br/><span style="color: #4a3728;">贺兰灵墟</span></div>
            <div><span style="color: #9b8c7a;">品级</span><br/><span style="color: #4a3728;">甲下</span></div>
            <div><span style="color: #9b8c7a;">配型</span><br/><span style="color: #8b6914;">鉴定中</span></div>
