          <span style="color: #6b5d4a; font-size: 0.85rem;">缘号·甲辰001</span>
          <span style="color: #8b7a6a; font-size: 0.72rem; margin-left: 6px;">旅人</span>
          <span style="background: #e6eee6; color: #3d6b6b; font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 2px; margin-left: 6px;">已售</span>
          <span style="color: #9b8c7a; font-size: 0.72rem; float: right;">金身渡化 · 成交价48000</span>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #fefcf7; border: 1px solid #e0d5c0; border-radius: 4px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; opacity: 0.75;">
          <span style="color: #6b5d4a; font-size: 0.85rem;">缘号·甲辰002</span>
          <span style="color: #8b7a6a; font-size: 0.72rem; margin-left: 6px;">观星者</span>
          <span style="background: #f5eedf; color: #8b6914; font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 2px; margin-left: 6px;">已处理</span>
          <span style="color: #9b8c7a; font-size: 0.72rem; float: right;">金刚舍利一具 · 甘露二味 · 成交价135000</span>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #fefcf7; border: 1px solid #e0d5c0; border-radius: 4px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
